title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Basant thanks Gehna to bless him with a boy child. Gehna wants to be with her child but she is bound to her promise. Anandi takes responsibility of the baby's studies.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Gehna decides to leave the house as she had promised Dadisa that she would leave the house after giving birth. Later, Dadisa asks Sumitra to convince Gehna not to leave the house and her baby.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Dadisa is grateful to Gehna for giving her a grandson. Anandi's family celebrates Gehna's son's naming ceremony. Dadisa welcomes her grandson by organizing a Dahi handi competition at the temple.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: The family organizes the Matki Phod competition and dance programs to celebrate Nandu's birthday. Later, Gehna plans to leave the house and hands over Nandu to Dadisa. Dadisa and Basant are absolutely shocked and request Gehna to stay.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Kalyani offers money to Gehna to take care of the child as a nanny. Gehna is offended. She ignores everyone's request and leaves the house.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Gehna walks out of the house leaving her newborn with Basant. Although Basant and the family plead with her, Gehna is adamant and leaves the house. She requests Bhairon to take care of Nandu.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Gehna goes back to her father's house. Her father yells at her for doing so, but her mother lets her stay. The baby keeps wailing, Basant is worried and goes to get Gehna back home.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Gehna denies to return home. For the sake of her dignity, halfheartedly Basant lets her go. Kalyani Devi curses Gehna and persuades Basant to forget her and move on for his son's sake.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Gehna's father convinces Gehna to stay back. Basant gets worried about his relationship. Basant Singh asks Niranjan to be Gehna's life partner.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Basant confesses about his relationship with Gehna to Niranjan. He talks about their disparities and how he failed to keep her happy. Later, Basant requests Niranjan to keep her happy and cheerful. Meanwhile, Kalyani's behaviour troubles Sumitra.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Sugna and Shyam visit Jagdish's house to meet Gehna and her child but Dadisa tells Sugna that Gehna is at her mother's place. Meanwhile Basant decides to divorce Gehna but Bhairon tells him that he will not let it happen.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Shyam and Sugna visit Gehna's house. Radha reaches home and inquires about Gehna. Basant tells Niranjan about the problems, he faces with Gehna and he asks Niranjan to marry her.
